name: The Bedroom Demos
description: It's a hard life, sitting in blankets and balancing keyboards on the biggest books you own. All to bring you a slice of demo pie. It's the first thing to be released from The Dishery, so to celebrate, we've made this CD. It's a hand numbered limited edition of 500. Get them before we're too famous; in years to come this little CD could be your Waikiki Retirement Fund. Listen at: http://soundcloud.com/thedishthespoon
